        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結　油價全星期狂升35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"659\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V80IwHgCOc2XuFxBxcc4tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b773aef0-19ab-11f1-b3b3-efcef343179f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日，星期五。關鍵的每月就業報告意外轉弱，市場對通脹的憂慮升溫，三大指數皆下跌。美股經歷動盪一周後，好消息是美股明天喘定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指下跌0.9%，即逾450點，是跌幅最少的指數；以科技股為主的納指數下跌約1.6%；標普500指數下跌1.3%。三大指數全周均錄得跌幅，標普500指數累跌2%，道指更挫3%，納指則跌約1%。而由年初至今亦已轉為下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因霍爾木茲海峽油輪運輸幾乎陷入停滯，市場擔心波斯灣出口國在儲存空間耗盡後可能被迫減產。同時，美國與以色列對伊朗的戰事仍未見緩和跡象，特朗普今天表示，解決衝突的唯一途徑是「無條件投降」。油價升至逾90元，全星期累計升幅高達35%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f4baba21-8022-4470-a2fa-a4e0070d16ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日（星期五）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌453.19點或0.95%，報47,501.55點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌90.69點或1.33%，報6,740.02點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌361.31點或1.59%，報22,387.68點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報91.27美元一桶，升10.26美元或12.67%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,181.3美元一盎司，升102.6美元或2.02%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報68,119.67美元，跌3,128.45美元或4.39%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.133厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月就業報告顯示，非農就業職位意外減少92,000個，遠遜於市場預期的新增55,000個；失業率亦上升至4.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勞動市場轉弱，加上中東衝突推高油價，令市場憂慮出現滯脹，亦即經濟增長疲弱與通脹上升同時出現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價狂升，航空股最為受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國航空;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAL/\">美國航空</a>(AAL.US)挫5.2%，美聯航(UAL.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:達美航空;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/DAL/\">達美航空</a>(DAL.US)均跌逾3%。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Caterpillar;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CAT/\">Caterpillar</a>(CAT.US)跌3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大型科技股走弱，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">英偉達</a>(NVDA.US)挫3%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>(META.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>(AMZN.US)、特斯拉(TSLA.US)均跌逾2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:蘋果;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL/\">蘋果</a>(AAPL.US)、Alphabet(GOOG.US)跌約1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特普在周五呼籲伊朗「無條件投降」，亦會晤多家美國主要國防承包商高層，包括<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:16;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Lockheed Martin;cpos:16;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/LMT/\">Lockheed Martin</a>(LMT.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:17;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:波音;cpos:17;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BA/\">波音</a>(BA.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:18;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:RTX;cpos:18;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/RTX/\">RTX</a>(RTX.US)及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:19;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Northrop Grumman;cpos:19;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOC/\">Northrop Grumman</a>(NOC.US)等軍工商。相關軍工股普遍升約2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外界憂慮隨著對伊朗戰事持續接近一周且未見結束跡象，美軍武器庫存正逐步消耗，白宮則淡化武器庫存下降的憂慮，強調美軍軍火庫存充足。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C-%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%B5%82%E7%B5%90-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%85%A8%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E7%8B%82%E5%8D%8735-223632886.html",
